  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/dfb45bbc3c9abe15e665bea83529e17e.webp?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Launch yourself into a puzzle-filled labyrinth as Horace Hagfish. Your expertise in slime production and love for meat render you the perfect candidate to recover the colors of the cosmos. Eat colorful meat to generate colorized slime trails, blend colors to shift hues, and collect chromatic orbs to unlock the exit. Remember to be mindful of your mixing, as creating brown is game over for both you and the cosmos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/98a74cf7b1bb328c24cd95b92a47c988.poster.avif?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/98a74cf7b1bb328c24cd95b92a47c988.webm?t=1702950714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/98a74cf7b1bb328c24cd95b92a47c988.mp4?t=1702950714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Eat meat to create colorized slime trails. Blend colors by crossing paths!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/33e449a5199d1477f4dc45e7ae23fd16.poster.avif?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/33e449a5199d1477f4dc45e7ae23fd16.webm?t=1702950714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/33e449a5199d1477f4dc45e7ae23fd16.mp4?t=1702950714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Whatever you do, don't make brown!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/0b914988f5f55f6e55fdaf00bbe48874.webp?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Experience 50 levels that will push your wits to the limit.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A cornucopia of innovative puzzle elements.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Glorious 16-color EGA graphics!</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>If you find yourself stuck, a progressive hint system will guide you in the right direction.</strong></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/4f7af441d9317ecf5bbd5ccd10b677c0.webp?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br>Monochromulus has broken free of the CGA nebula and extended his Proboscis-Umbilicus toward the peaceful planet of EGA…<br>With a suction, only pure evil can muster, Monochromulus sucks up the color orbs and delicious meats of EGA. For he loathes the vibrant colors of the cosmos and intends to mix them all together and cover the universe in brown techno gravy. Only you can save the universe from a monochromatic gravy drenched future!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600050/extras/a6a66c21e1a8c14f9f4ea96ab76424be.avif?t=1702950714\" width=616 height=400 /></span>",
